    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/109e8783e3eac8f1c5fb33a645e453e2.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Milly’s Meadow is a relaxing idle game that sits on your desktop. You can resize it and place it anywhere to create the perfect peaceful backdrop for your day. Milly moves through the meadow on her own. Interaction is minimal, with no tasks and no pressure. Just watch, listen, and enjoy the soothing sounds of nature, gentle activities, and original lo-fi tunes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/778171f2b5832bd2e376e0632c10def9.poster.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/778171f2b5832bd2e376e0632c10def9.webm?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/778171f2b5832bd2e376e0632c10def9.mp4?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/91b6c4866568727fe4d3094bc17f5cf9.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock optional outfits to customise Milly and match your mood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/9efb1a72472f51db1292cffc015e58d6.poster.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/9efb1a72472f51db1292cffc015e58d6.webm?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/9efb1a72472f51db1292cffc015e58d6.mp4?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/b55197f577e6455a28a9a714d2dbcb1e.poster.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/b55197f577e6455a28a9a714d2dbcb1e.webm?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/b55197f577e6455a28a9a714d2dbcb1e.mp4?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/f4bfc6ad89a56e4d5156982384753b61.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock optional decorations to design the meadow the way you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/96258d906c9dfea691564efe72228c25.poster.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/96258d906c9dfea691564efe72228c25.webm?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/96258d906c9dfea691564efe72228c25.mp4?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/cc22ff600909d250b3180342ed49613c.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add optional activities to your meadow for Milly to enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/821666893fbcfb0205cd6edf1245a794.poster.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/821666893fbcfb0205cd6edf1245a794.webm?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/821666893fbcfb0205cd6edf1245a794.mp4?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/92138f19f58b83853ec70c878f34461d.poster.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/92138f19f58b83853ec70c878f34461d.webm?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/92138f19f58b83853ec70c878f34461d.mp4?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/0a8898b566c57a5d218466107b3122ae.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Milly's Meadow sits on top (or behind) your applications while you work or unwind. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/248b0b5b228d71aa99a6386796d49cfc.poster.avif?t=1756476937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/248b0b5b228d71aa99a6386796d49cfc.webm?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063730/extras/248b0b5b228d71aa99a6386796d49cfc.mp4?t=1756476937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
